	<center>
		<h1>Constructing indexes</h1>
		<hr>

	</center>
	
	<p>
		To find results in a reasonable amount of time we need a quicker search method
		than just looking at each document individually.
	</p>
	<p>
		An <strong>index</strong> maps information in a corpus to a format that allows 
		quick location of specific content.
	</p>
	
